temperature <- 
  temperature %>%
  group_by(ISO3) %>%
  mutate(lag.popgrw = dplyr::lag(popgrw, n = 1, default = NA)) %>%
  mutate(lag.temp.temp = dplyr::lag(temp.temp, n = 1, default = NA)) %>%
  mutate(longtermlag = dplyr::lag(lagtemp, n = 3, default = NA)) %>%
  mutate(longtermlag_squared = dplyr::lag(lagtemp*lagtemp, n = 3, default = NA))
